HSN


	HSN was founded 37 years ago as the first shopping network and is headquartered in St. Petersburg, FL. HSN is a leading interactive multichannel retailer offering a curated assortment of exclusive products and top brand names to its customers. HSN incorporates entertainment, inspiration, personalities and industry experts to provide an entirely unique shopping experience. At HSN, customers find exceptional selections in the following categories:

Home / Lifestyle
	Bissell, Concierge Collection, iRobot, Hoover, Jeffrey Banks, Joy Mangano, Keith Urban, Origami, Samantha Brown …

Health & Beauty 
	Andrew Lessman, Benefit Cosmetics, Carol's Daughter, Elizabeth Arden, Fitbit, Jose Eber, Korres, Lancôme, OPI, Perlier, Serious Skincare, Signature Club A, Trish McEvoy, Too Faced, ybf Beauty ...

Culinary
	Calphalon, Char-Broil, Cuisinart, Curtis Stone, Rick Bayless, David’s Cookies, De’Longhi, Ferris Coffee & Nut Co., Kimberly Schlapman, Lorena Garcia, Ming Tsai, Nutribullet, Wolfgang Puck ...

Fashion / Accessories
	Melissa McCarthy, Sheryl Crow, Danica Patrick, Hillary Scott, Diane Gilman, Giuliana Rancic, Hal Rubenstein, IMAN, Sam Edelman, Serena Williams, Sharif, Steve Madden, Twiggy, Vince Camuto ...

Jewelry
	Amedeo Scognamiglio, King Baby, Carol Brodie, Emma Skye, Heidi Daus, Iris Apfel, Jay King, Jean Dousset, Joan Boyce, Kristin Chenoweth, R.J. Graziano, Victoria Wieck ...

Electronics
	Amazon, Acer, Apple, Beats by Dr. Dre, Canon, Fuji, GE, GOPRO, HP, JVC, LG, Nintendo, Panasonic, Samsung, Sony …

 











