Corporate Profile


	HSN, Inc. (Nasdaq: HSNI) is a $4 billion interactive multi-channel retailer with strong direct-to-consumer expertise and operates two business segments, HSN and Cornerstone.

	A leader in transactional innovation, HSN is the only retailer offering live streaming video on three screens – TV, online and mobile. HSN broadcasts live to 95 million households in the US in HD 24/7, and its web site – hsn.com – features more than 50,000 product videos. Mobile applications include HSN apps for iPad®, iPhone®, Android™, and HSN on Demand®.

	Cornerstone is comprised of interactive, aspirational home and apparel lifestyle brands including Frontgate, Ballard Designs, Garnet Hill, Grandin Road, and Improvements. Cornerstone operates separate e-commerce sites for all the brands, distributes more than 325 million catalogs annually, and has 14 retail and outlet stores.

	With principal offices in St. Petersburg, FL, HSNi employs approximately 6,900 employees.

	 


